data.description: Welcome to this cutie five-bedroom brick home nestled in the heart of Monticello, where beauty meets functionality. This property presents a unique opportunity with its thoughtfully designed in-law suite, offering versatile living arrangements for extended family or guests. As you step through the inviting front entrance, you'll immediately appreciate the timeless appeal of brick construction, showcasing both durability and elegance. The main residence boasts 3 bedrooms and 2 full tile bathrooms. The warmth of hardwood floors flows seamlessly throughout, enhancing the character of this charming home. In the kitchen you'll find stainless appliances and seating area. You'll also find plenty of storage space in the large, easily accessible attic. The living room is large yet cozy with a fireplace with plenty of natural light flowing in. A truly exceptional feature of this property is the well-appointed in-law suite. With its private entrance, it provides a sense of independence while remaining integrated with the main residence. The suite includes TWO generously sized bedroom, a modern bathroom, and a cozy living area. The kitchenette offers convenience and autonomy to its occupants, ensuring a comfortable and welcoming living experience. Step outside to discover an outdoor entertaining space that's big enough for everyone! The large backyard provides a great space for fun while the patio provides an ideal setting for al fresco dining and relaxation. This cutie home is perfectly situated just outside of downtown Monticello- don't miss it!
